OL,3,CMinisters urged to act quickly on
OL,4,Cstate pension communication
OL,5,Ccompensation plans
OL,7,FThe Government is being pressed by MPs
OL,8,Fto bring proposals forward before the
OL,9,Fsummer recess to provide compensation
OL,10,Ffor women affected by failures to
OL,11,Fcommunicate increases in the state
OL,12,Fpension age.
OL,14,FIn a report published in March, the
OL,15,FParliamentary and Health Service
OL,16,FOmbudsman (PHSO) asked Parliament to
OL,17,Fidentify how to provide an appropriate
OL,18,Fremedy for those who have suffered
OL,19,Finjustice because of maladministration
OL,20,Fon the part of the Department for Work
OL,21,Fand Pensions (DWP).
