OL,7,FThe letter says: "As you are aware,
OL,8,Fthe PHSO laid its report before
OL,9,FParliament on March 21 2024, asking
OL,10,FParliament to 'identify an appropriate
OL,11,Fmechanism for providing remedy" for
OL,12,Fwomen born in the 1950s who have
OL,13,Fsuffered injustice because of DWP's
OL,14,Fmaladministration in its communication
OL,15,Fof increases in their state pension
OL,16,Fage (SPA) legislated for in the
OL,17,FPensions Act 1995.
OL,26,@oD@ROUsD@_O]
