OL,7,FThe letter highlighted evidence from
OL,8,FAngela Madden, chairwoman of the Waspi
OL,9,Fcampaign.
OL,11,FShe previously told the committee that
OL,12,Fwomen's divorce settlements had been
OL,13,Fbased on a pension age of 60, meaning
OL,14,Fthey had been awarded less money.
OL,16,FThe letter added: "Implementing a
OL,17,Fremedy will need parliamentary time,
OL,18,Ffinancial resources, and the data and
OL,19,Ftechnical systems only available to
OL,20,Fyour department.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
