OL,4,Cstate pension communication
OL,5,Ccompensation plans
OL,7,F"It cannot happen without Government
OL,8,Fsupport. We would ask you to bring
OL,9,Fforward proposals for a remedy by the
OL,10,Fsummer recess."
OL,12,FThe ombudsman's report suggested that
OL,13,Fcompensation at level four, ranging
OL,14,Fbetween #1,000 and #2,950, could be
OL,15,Fappropriate for each of those affected.
OL,17,FSpeaking in the House of Commons in
OL,18,FMarch, Mr Stride said there will be a
OL,19,Ffull and proper consideration of the
OL,20,Fombudsman's report.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@OO]
