OL,7,FHe said: "When considering the DWP's
OL,8,Factions between August 2005 and
OL,9,FDecember 2007, the ombudsman came to
OL,10,Fthe view that those actions resulted
OL,11,Fin 1950s-born women receiving
OL,12,Findividual notice later than they
OL,13,Fmight, had different decisions been
OL,14,Fmade."
