OL,7,FSpeaking about the letter, Sir Stephen
OL,8,Fsaid: "The debate over the impact of
OL,9,Fthe DWP's failure to communicate
OL,10,Fincreases in the women's state pension
OL,11,Fage has dragged on for too long and it
OL,12,Fis time the Government took action to
OL,13,Fresolve the issue.
OL,15,F"There is no perfect solution, but
OL,16,Fthere would seem to be broad support
OL,17,Ffor a rules-based system of
OL,18,Fcompensation with a degree of
OL,19,Fflexibility for cases where women have
OL,20,Fexperienced direct financial loss.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
