OL,7,F"The committee is right to suggest
OL,8,Fthere must be additional compensation
OL,9,Ffor those many hundreds of thousands
OL,10,Fwho suffered direct financial loss in
OL,11,Faddition to a fixed sum for all those
OL,12,Faffected by successive governments'
OL,13,Ffailures.
OL,15,F"After years of campaigning, both the
OL,16,Findependent ombudsman and now a cross-
OL,17,Fparty group of senior MPs have
OL,18,Fvindicated our position.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
