OL,7,F"For ministers to leave setting up a
OL,8,Fcompensation scheme a moment longer is
OL,9,Fjust delaying the inevitable and
OL,10,Finsulting our generation of women
OL,11,Fafresh."
OL,13,FA DWP spokesperson said: "We are
OL,14,Fconsidering the Ombudsman's report and
OL,15,Fwill respond in due course, having
OL,16,Fcooperated fully throughout this
OL,17,Finvestigation.
