OL,7,F"The government has always been
OL,8,Fcommitted to supporting all pensioners
OL,9,Fin a sustainable way that gives them a
OL,10,Fdignified retirement whilst also being
OL,11,Ffair to them and taxpayers.
OL,13,F"The State Pension is the foundation
OL,14,Fof income in retirement and will
OL,15,Fremain so as we delivered a further
OL,16,F8.5% rise last month, increasing the
OL,17,Fstate pension for 12 million
OL,18,Fpensioners. This has seen the full
OL,19,Frate of the new State Pension rise by
OL,20,F#900."
